          TerraLib 5 - Apache CouchDB Data Access Driver
          ==============================================
          
This folder contains an implementation of the Data Access classes
for the Apache CouchDB, a document store database system.

Driver Dependencies:
--------------------

This driver requires the following modules in order to be built:
1. Common Runtime
2. XML
3. Plugin
4. Data Type
5. SRS
6. Geometry
7. Raster
8. Data Access

The third-party software needed:
1. libcURL

More Information:
-----------------

The TerraLib 5 wiki contains a complete explanation about
the internals of this driver:
http://www.dpi.inpe.br/terralib5/wiki/doku.php?id=wiki:designimplementation:dataaccess:drivers:couchdb


